pplying the machinery developed herein to bound the Borel\ncomplexity of several well-studied classification problems in mathematics, such\nas that of automorphisms of continuous-trace $C^{*}$-algebras up to unitary\nequivalence, or that of Hermitian line bundles, up to isomorphism, over a\nlocally compact second countable space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Sep 2019 06:11:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 14 Sep 2019 03:19:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-17"}
