ur simulations. Thus, the existence of\nJupiter is the key parameter for specifying when and where chondrule formation\noccurs for impact-based scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Sep 2019 06:46:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Sep 2019 01:01:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-16"}
