that the Fermi pockets almost\ndisappear in NaNd2NiO4 and NaCa2NiO3.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Sep 2019 15:43:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Nov 2019 03:35:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-02"}
